default 
defaultGovernance needs 
defaultrevisiting for primary schools. : Sponsored chains are more likely to have ‘professional’ or highly skilled governors which work across schools enabling them to have an overview of the locality of schools. Higher skill sets can also lead to their being mor
defaulte effective in holding school leadership to account.
